title: Purchase delay won’t hurt Chateau Theatre revamp in Rochester
text: Apartment Sales Tracker Home / News / Purchase delay won’t hurt Chateau Theatre revamp in Rochester The Chateau Theatre in downtown Rochester, at 15 First St. SW, didn’t switch owners Friday as expected, but city officials say a month delay in closing the city’s $6 million purchase won’t affect plans to restore the property to a new use. Submitted photo: Chad Johnson Purchase delay won’t hurt Chateau Theatre revamp in Rochester By: Karlee Weinmann October 16, 2015 5:49 pm 0 It could be another month before the city of Rochester seals its $6 million purchase of the historic Chateau Theatre.
